  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3231790e42d9ef147be92c6486395585, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  deathTexts:
  - "You thought you were an astronaut\u2026 turns out you're just space debris now."
  - "Nice jump! Too bad the asteroid didn\u2019t agree.  "
  - 'Gravity? Never heard of it. Oh wait, now you have.  '
  - 'That was a bold move. Boldly falling into the void.  '
  - "Bro really thought he had it. Spoiler: He didn\u2019t.  "
  - 'Skill issue detected. Recommended fix: Stop missing.  '
  - "That asteroid wasn\u2019t even far. How did you mess that up?  "
  - "If I had a dollar for every time you missed, I\u2019d buy a planet.  "
  - 'At this point, even a space rock has better movement.  '
  - "NASA just called. You\u2019re fired.  "
  - "The stars are watching\u2026 and they\u2019re disappointed.  "
  - "Space is infinite, but your chances of landing clearly aren\u2019t.  "
  - 'Maybe next time aim for the asteroid instead of disappointment.  '
  - 'That was a perfect demonstration of how NOT to jump.  '
  - 'That was a perfect demonstration of how NOT to jump.  '
  - "You're like a satellite\u2026 except you crash instead of orbit.  "
  - '"Trust the jump," they said. Bad advice.  '
  - "I\u2019ve seen space dust survive longer than you.  "
  - "That asteroid was stationary. What\u2019s your excuse?  "
  - 'Maybe if you miss enough times, you''ll land in an alternate universe where
    you''re good at this.  '
